==English==

===Etymology===
From the verb ''to [[bob]]'' + [[-er]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{cattag|fishing}} A [[buoyant]] device (frequently made of [[cork]]) attached to a [[line]] so as to suspend the end of the line with the [[hook]] (and [[bait]] or [[lure]]) above the bottom.


